    {
      "id": "PopularPost375169",
      "post_content": "You can:  \nCast it during your upkeep to effectively take an extra turn.  \nCast it in response to a spell to counter that spell, even if it's uncounterable.  \nCast it in response to an creature attacking to prevent the damage.  \nCast it in response to an ability activating or triggering to counter that ability.  \nCast it in response to your own \"at the beginning of the next end step\" to keep a temporary creature indefinitely.  \nCast it in response to storm nonsense to eliminate the entire storm stack.  \nCast it when nothing is going on, just to be classy.",
      "posted_by": "Atali",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost375169\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_post\">You can:<br/>Cast it during your upkeep to effectively take an extra turn.<br/>Cast it in response to a spell to counter that spell, even if it's uncounterable.<br/>Cast it in response to an creature attacking to prevent the damage.<br/>Cast it in response to an ability activating or triggering to counter that ability.<br/>Cast it in response to your own \"at the beginning of the next end step\" to keep a temporary creature indefinitely.<br/>Cast it in response to storm nonsense to eliminate the entire storm stack.<br/>Cast it when nothing is going on, just to be classy.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '375169'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy42588\">Atali</span>\r\n                                (5/8/2014 10:31:07 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSm